name: Space Kitten (itaypoo)
description:
You and your kitten are in space, and you must continue moving using your teleport gun while keeping your kitten safe.

Find cat food floating in space and feed it to your cat to get a card that will give you a random power up.

Made for the Extra Credits Game Jam #6
